OL,3,C'Bankrupt' Birmingham confirms #148m
OL,4,Cof council cuts in second budget blow
OL,6,FThe announcement confirms what many
OL,7,Fresidents feared: another year of
OL,8,Ffinancial turmoil, deepening service
OL,9,Fcuts, and higher council tax.
OL,11,FFor those who depend on adult social
OL,12,Fcare, public transport subsidies, or
OL,13,Fessential community services, the
OL,14,Flatest round of cuts is a stark
OL,15,Freminder that the worst is not yet
OL,16,Fover.
OL,18,FThis is the council's second budget
OL,19,Fsince declaring effective bankruptcy
OL,20,Fin 2023. It says it needs to save
OL,21,F#300m over two years.
