OL,6,F"A perfect storm of dysfunction"
OL,8,FThe authority says it has lost one
OL,9,Fbillion pounds from central government
OL,10,Fsince 2010 but yesterday confirmed
OL,11,Fthat it has been given an extra #120m
OL,12,Fof core spending power - up 8.9% on
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,FThe situation in Birmingham is a case
OL,16,Fstudy in how local government
OL,17,Fausterity, financial mismanagement,
OL,18,Fand economic pressures converge to
OL,19,Fcreate a perfect storm of dysfunction.
